程序包的使用
application.model

  • application.model使用的application.model中的类 
    类和说明
    Bomb
    Set the location, radius and image of the bomb.
    Cookie
    Set the location, radius, value, image of the cookie.
    Draw
    This class is used to draw the board of the game with the cookies, ghost, hearts, bombs and the pacman.
    Generate
    Generate ghosts, cookies and hearts for pacman.
    Ghost
    This class provides the methods to support the basic algorithms for all kinds of ghosts.
    Heart
    Set the location, radius and image of the heart.
    Maze
    Generate the maze for pacman.
    Music
    this class is used to turn on and turn off the background music.
    Score
    This class create a object Score with combination of two texts (score and lifes).
